# One file per business responsibility

## Frontend (Inertia/Vue)

- **One component per file**: every Vue component must live in its own `.vue` file.
- If a page/layout grows, **extract dedicated components** under `inertia/components/**` rather than keeping large blocks inline.

## Backend (AdonisJS)

- **One business responsibility per file** (services/controllers/jobs/helpers).
- If a service/controller/job becomes large, **split by business function** into smaller files.
- Avoid “god files” that mix unrelated business concerns.

